{"tid":495750,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有人吞咗我一隻兔仔","createTime":"2017-12-11T03:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T17:07:39.000Z","uid":80951,"like":3,"dislike":68,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"ebd83fdea43cb697d9a3a8884d3cd0763c2a4c7b","tid":495750,"uid":80951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T03:50:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的 男朋友有養緊一對兔仔<br />\n之前連續俾佢roommate個女朋友炮轟兔仔甩毛<br />\n無辦法之下透過facebook將兔仔交咗俾人領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一個星期都未到 我今日喺facebook見到個領養人放返其中一隻兔仔出嚟求領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原因話屋企人有嚴重兔毛敏感 但領養時明明講之前養過兔仔<br />\n<br />\n對兔仔由細到大都一齊成長 之前我已經好唔想放出去俾人領養 而家仲要發生件咁嘅事 我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2648c46008410c8bc86d21a2cec04a33babd557d","tid":495750,"uid":116905,"like":104,"dislike":2,"score":102,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T03:55:10.000Z","msg":"平胸港女患語癌<br />\n甩毛兔仔求領養"},{"pid":"08c8e9adf8ff0e70ff477212009c3501f8361a4a","tid":495750,"uid":80951,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T03:55:12.000Z","msg":"推~ 係未我個topic開得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158b6900890ceff5efe39a7fb02d788c417077b4","tid":495750,"uid":80951,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T03:57:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平胸港女患語癌<br />\n甩毛兔仔求領養</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係未平胸港女語癌都無所謂了<br />\n最重要係我可以做到啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f46d34fc0d4ecebae0e57684a1f1082a224efc","tid":495750,"uid":162016,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T03:58:11.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"4548dbec71c6bd3103